1
00:00:09,090 --> 00:00:11,180
W-Wait, Akari.

2
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:14,930
Oh... sorry.

3
00:00:16,560 --> 00:00:19,560
Actually, I came with my husband...

4
00:00:19,650 --> 00:00:20,690
What?!

5
00:00:21,730 --> 00:00:26,320
Oh... it is late, isn't it? 
Sorry.

6
00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:32,950
How did you get here?
Train? Taxi?

7
00:00:33,370 --> 00:00:34,740
By taxi.

8
00:00:35,410 --> 00:00:40,040
And... I asked my husband to wait 
for me at the station for now.

9
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:45,670
Geez...
You should've told me this before coming.

10
00:00:46,300 --> 00:00:48,010
I'm sorry.

11
00:00:50,630 --> 00:00:54,050
No... I'm the one who's wrong.

12
00:00:59,020 --> 00:01:04,440
I'm sorry for acting so childish
 and causing you trouble.

13
00:01:15,370 --> 00:01:16,490
Oh...

14
00:01:18,250 --> 00:01:20,830
You came because 
you were worried about me, right?

15
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:23,790
Thank you.

16
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:26,460
I'm fine.

17
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,630
Please apologize to your husband for me.

18
00:01:33,050 --> 00:01:35,600
What?! No, what are you doing? 
You're scaring me.

19
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:39,100
I'm sorry for being dishonest.

20
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:41,730
But I'm going to be honest now.

21
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:52,610
I'm really overwhelmed 
by my feelings right now.

22
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:57,490
I don't know why I'm so drawn to you.

23
00:01:57,580 --> 00:02:00,910
Even today, I couldn't sit still...

24
00:02:08,170 --> 00:02:09,460
Come in.

25
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:50,000
Damn it,

26
00:02:51,130 --> 00:02:52,590
you seducer.

27
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:57,720
No one has ever said things 
like that to me before.

28
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:01,680
I'm actually quite reserved, usually...

29
00:03:36,260 --> 00:03:37,720
Welcome!

30
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,510
Sorry for making you wait.

31
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:45,350
No, I was just having a drink anyway.

32
00:03:57,450 --> 00:03:58,610
Did you talk to her?

33
00:04:00,950 --> 00:04:02,080
Yeah.

34
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:09,210
Still in love with her, I take it?

35
00:04:14,510 --> 00:04:17,970
Don't just stay silent. 
Deny it, at least.

36
00:04:28,520 --> 00:04:30,520
Thank you for letting me go.

37
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,610
It's nothing...

38
00:04:40,700 --> 00:04:45,070
If something happened, I'd be the one
 who couldn't sleep at night anyway.

39
00:04:52,540 --> 00:04:55,130
Why did it have to be a woman?

40
00:04:55,210 --> 00:04:57,130
Of all things...

41
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:18,110
I'm sorry.

42
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:22,820
Please go ahead with the divorce.

43
00:05:35,090 --> 00:05:37,220
You don't get to decide that.

44
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:42,590
I mean, you cheated, right?

45
00:05:43,340 --> 00:05:44,600
You had an affair, right?

46
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:52,350
I won't divorce you.

47
00:06:04,570 --> 00:06:07,120
Let's go. 
Let's go home.

48
